name: Gemah Rupa Loh Jinawi
description:
Indonesia is a country that is peaceful, prosperous, and has abundant natural wealth.
or what is often called "Gemah Ripah Loh Jinawi".
This illustration work entitled "Gemah Rupa Loh Jinawi" represents the wealth of art, especially Indonesian art. The wealth of works of art can be manifested in various kinds of fine arts such as batik, traditional ornaments that are characteristic of Indonesia.
